title: Tumi Alpha 2 Three Way Brief 26180 - Overview
description:
Tumi Alpha 2 Three Way Brief - 26180 - BLACK
http://www.abt.com/product/96391/Tumi-26180BLACK.html?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=video&utm_campaign=026180D2_20160302

TUMI elevates your travel and business experience with Alpha 2 the pinnacle of our design innovation engineering functionality and performance. The Three-Way Brief offers the multitasking business traveler the utmost in versatility with the option to carry this style as a brief backpack or tote.
Features:
• Primary Material: Ballistic Nylon  
• Fits: up to 15
• Laptop Dimensions:
o H: 10.25
o W: 14.75
o D: 1.5
• Interior:
o Padded 15 laptop pocket with removable padded side bumpers
o Multiple open/zip pockets
o Zip pocket with TUMI ID™ Lock protective lining
o Cellphone pocket
o 2 elastic media pockets
o 3 business card pockets
o Pen loops/Key leash
• Exterior:
o Leather top carry handles
o Webbing side carry handle
o Detachable shoulder strap with shoulder pad
o Zip entry to main compartments
o Adjustable backpack straps tuck away when not in use
o Waterproof front U-zip pocket
o Multiple front and back pockets
